      BEFORE PUBLISHING EACH RELEASE update the <item> below:
        1. title       — human-readable version ("Version 1.2.3")
        2. sparkle:version             — CFBundleVersion (integer build number)
        3. sparkle:shortVersionString  — CFBundleShortVersionString ("1.2.3")
        4. pubDate     — release date in RFC 822 format
        5. description — release notes (HTML inside CDATA is fine)
        6. enclosure url=    — public HTTPS URL of the notarized .pkg
        7. enclosure length= — byte size: stat -f%z InterlinedList.pkg
        8. sparkle:edSignature= — output of:
               <sparkle-checkout>/bin/sign_update InterlinedList.pkg <private-key>

      Publish this file to: https://interlinedlist.com/appcast.xml
    -->

